Package: ctww
Title: Camera Trap Workflow Wrapper
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robert",
           family = "Ritson",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "robert.ritson@idfg.idaho.gov")
Description: A collection of functions supporting a workflow pipeline for remote 
    cameras used in wildlife monitoring. Created specifically with IDFG projects in mind. 
    Includes wrappers for Microsoft's MegaDetector and MegaClassifier as well as R-translations
    of the original Python-based functions.
SystemRequirements: Python3.7, Anaconda3
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    reticulate,
    stringr
Author: Robert Ritson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Robert Ritson <robert.ritson@idfg.idaho.gov>
